Here's a PlantUML component diagram focusing on the deployment aspect of the CPR2U system:

```plantuml
@startuml dsc-sookmyung_2023-mention-all-SolutionChallenge

!define GCP #4285F4
!define FIREBASE #FFA000
!define ANDROID #3DDC84
!define IOS #000000
!define SPRING #6DB33F

skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor<<GCP>> GCP
  BorderColor<<GCP>> #3367D6
  BackgroundColor<<FIREBASE>> FIREBASE
  BorderColor<<FIREBASE>> #F57C00
  BackgroundColor<<ANDROID>> ANDROID
  BorderColor<<ANDROID>> #3DDC84
  BackgroundColor<<IOS>> IOS
  BorderColor<<IOS>> #000000
  BackgroundColor<<SPRING>> SPRING
  BorderColor<<SPRING>> #4F9E4F
}

cloud "Google Cloud Platform" {
  [Google Kubernetes Engine] <<GCP>> as GKE
  [Cloud SQL] <<GCP>>
  [Google Maps API] <<GCP>>
}

cloud "Firebase" {
  [Firebase Auth] <<FIREBASE>>
  [Firebase Cloud Messaging] <<FIREBASE>>
  [Firebase Realtime Database] <<FIREBASE>>
}

node "Mobile Devices" {
  [Android App] <<ANDROID>>
  [iOS App] <<IOS>>
}

node "Backend Server" {
  [Spring Boot Application] <<SPRING>>
}

[Android App] --> [Firebase Auth]: Authenticates
[Android App] --> [Firebase Cloud Messaging]: Receives notifications
[Android App] --> [Firebase Realtime Database]: Real-time updates
[Android App] --> [Google Maps API]: Location services

[iOS App] --> [Firebase Auth]: Authenticates
[iOS App] --> [Firebase Cloud Messaging]: Receives notifications
[iOS App] --> [Firebase Realtime Database]: Real-time updates
[iOS App] --> [Google Maps API]: Location services

[Spring Boot Application] --> [Firebase Cloud Messaging]: Sends notifications
[Spring Boot Application] --> [Google Maps API]: Geocoding & routing

GKE --> [Spring Boot Application]: Hosts
[Spring Boot Application] --> [Cloud SQL]: Persists data

[Android App] --> [Spring Boot Application]: API calls
[iOS App] --> [Spring Boot Application]: API calls

@enduml
```